												a(href="assets/images/content/steps-img/faq-steps-obs-03.jpg").faq-step__preview
													img( src="assets/images/content/steps-img/faq-steps-obs-03.jpg" alt="")
											.faq-step
												.faq-step__name 4. Возьми URL и ключ Стрима в настройках канала
												a(href="assets/images/content/steps-img/faq-steps-obs-04.jpg").faq-step__preview
													img( src="assets/images/content/steps-img/faq-steps-obs-04.jpg" alt="")
											.faq-step
												.faq-step__name 5. Вставь URL и Stream key
